<h2>What is KoiChan?</h2>
<p>Koichan exists to combat the deterioration of life and to build ourselves into positive forces in this mad, mad world.</p>
<p>Specifically, KoiChan attempts to combine the greatest aspects of imageboards and classic webforums to foster a non-toxic community of freethinkers for the educational, artistic, spiritual, and physical improvement of us all.</p>
<p>In pursuit of this ideal, I kindly ask that you read the guidelines below before posting.</p>
