<div class="row">
    <div class="col-8">
        <h4 class="homeSubheader">Guidelines</h4>
        <p>If you are not here for open-minded discussion, or to self-improve and/or help others, BEGONE!</p>
        <p>No lazyposting! Iron sharpens iron. You get what you give!</p>
        <p>No rudeposting! Constructive criticism only. BAD: "This is stupid." GOOD: "This is stupid because..."</p>
        <p>No lewdposting! There are many other sites for that. This is not one of them. Keep it clean!</p>
        <p>On politicalposting: Unfounded generalized statements about any racial/ethnic group is not tolerated. Either elaborate or cite your sources.</p>
        <p>And of course: NOTHING ILLEGAL!</p>
        <p>Happy posting!!</p>
    </div>
